      "difficulty": "warmup",
      "source": "in the style of Stewart 8e, chapter 10"
    },
    {
      "id": "calculus-ii-conic-sections-006",
      "stem": "Find the eccentricity of the ellipse $\\dfrac{x^2}{169} + \\dfrac{y^2}{144} = 1$.",
